---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';

const description = "Terms of use for AI Lean Solutions LLC and its public website.";
---

<Base title="Terms" description={description}>

  <section class="pt-16 pb-24 md:pt-24 md:pb-32">
    <div class="container-site max-w-prose">

      <p class="section-label mb-4">// Legal</p>
      <h1 class="font-display font-bold tracking-tightest text-[clamp(2rem,5vw,3.5rem)] leading-[1.05]">
        Terms of use
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-[14px] text-text-muted font-mono">
        Last updated: June 2026
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-8 text-[16px] leading-relaxed text-white/85">

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">1. What this site is</h2>
          <p>
            AILeanSolutions.com is the parent-company website for AI Lean Solutions LLC. It
            points visitors to our active public initiatives: AI Promotion Guy and UsefulOps AI.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">2. Separate services</h2>
          <p>
            AI Promotion Guy and UsefulOps AI may include their own intake forms, offers,
            payment terms, or client agreements. If you engage one of those services, the terms
            presented there or in the related agreement control that service.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">3. Informational content</h2>
          <p>
            Content on this site and linked initiative sites is provided for general information
            and practical education. It is not legal, financial, medical, regulatory, or other
            professional advice.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">4. Acceptable use</h2>
          <p>
            Do not misuse the site, attempt to disrupt it, submit unlawful material, or use
            forms or contact channels to send spam, malicious code, or abusive content.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">5. Accuracy</h2>
          <p>
            We try to keep public information accurate and current, but we may update, revise,
            or remove content at any time. Use your own judgment before acting on anything you
            read.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">6. Third-party links</h2>
          <p>
            This site links to other sites, including our initiative domains. We are not
            responsible for third-party websites or services outside our control.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">7. Limitation of liability</h2>
          <p>
            To the fullest extent permitted by law, our liability for any claim arising from
            use of this site is limited to the amount you paid us for use of this site, if any.
            We are not liable for indirect, incidental, consequential, or special damages.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">8. Governing law</h2>
          <p>
            These terms are governed by the laws of the State of California, and any dispute
            will be resolved in the state or federal courts located in Sacramento County,
            California.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">9. Changes</h2>
          <p>
            We may update these terms from time to time. The current version will be posted
            here with the updated date.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">10. Contact</h2>
          <p>
            Questions go to
            <a href="mailto:Brian.Bricker@AILeansolutions.com" class="underline underline-offset-4 decoration-white/30 hover:decoration-white">Brian.Bricker@AILeansolutions.com</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Base>
